{"tid":1125171,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TWICE走紅毯慘跌 子瑜轉身神救援","createTime":"2019-04-25T13:47:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-27T20:49:24.000Z","uid":231132,"like":6,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2bb5b225804abecd405c77173ee93f9c3a505bb6","tid":1125171,"uid":231132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T13:47:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/ent/page/800/2019/04/25/phpqmF3n4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fent%2Fpage%2F800%2F2019%2F04%2F25%2FphpqmF3n4.jpg&h=3c0b003d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTWICE 24日出席頒獎典禮。（翻攝自推特）<br />\n<br />\n南韓人氣女團TWICE，昨（24日）出席頒獎典禮，9妞以黑白造型登場，Sana走紅毯時，不慎跌倒，子瑜發現後，立即轉身獻救援，暖心之舉獲網友大讚。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/ent/page/800/2019/04/25/php3PN1n2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fent%2Fpage%2F800%2F2019%2F04%2F25%2Fphp3PN1n2.jpg&h=13052bc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSana走階梯不慎跌倒。（翻攝自韓網）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/ent/page/800/2019/04/25/php52zQtq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fent%2Fpage%2F800%2F2019%2F04%2F25%2Fphp52zQtq.jpg&h=a021378d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSana走紅毯不慎跌倒，子瑜轉身救援。（翻攝自韓網）<br />\n<br />\nSana身穿白色連身長裙搭配高跟鞋，渾身散發一股仙氣，疑因走階梯踩空，她當場跌倒，露出驚恐神情，走在前方的子瑜察覺不對勁，立即轉身攙扶，隊友及保安也向前關心，Sana雖跌倒出糗，但最後仍鎮定地走完紅毯。"},{"pid":"fc4808541c0cac02c7b875481c5c7285709b653c","tid":1125171,"uid":208486,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T14:02:50.000Z","msg":"善心打破0回覆"},{"pid":"3a8cce268d8afe837d7d1af7e99561cfa31f8f93","tid":1125171,"uid":55519,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T14:08:21.000Z","msg":"點解娜璉樣衰左"},{"pid":"6593ca57d68c3c44e7e6d8bb3e16a446d80ac939","tid":1125171,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T14:13:43.000Z","msg":"正喔"},{"pid":"26f9b1c48b328bcfc933fb8094e2d0